is.merkor.core.redis.dictionaries
Class MerkorRedisConstants

java.lang.Object
  is.merkor.core.redis.dictionaries.MerkorRedisConstants

public class MerkorRedisConstants
extends java.lang.Object

All constants used in the Redis representation of the MerkOr data. These are the key prefixes, followed by an id, a lemma, or a cluster name.

Version:
0.8
Author:
Anna B. Nikulasdottir

ID_KEY_PREFIX_IS

public static final java.lang.String ID_KEY_PREFIX_IS
The prefix for lemma id keys in MerkOr_IS_general. The value for a lexical item key is a hash with the fields 'lemma' and 'wordclass'.

REL_ID_PREFIX_IS

public static final java.lang.String REL_ID_PREFIX_IS
The prefix for relation id keys in MerkOr_IS_general. The value for a relation key is a hash with the fields 'from_item', 'to_item', 'relation', and 'score'.

SORTED_REL_SET_ID

public static final java.lang.String SORTED_REL_SET_ID
The prefix for sorted relation sets in MerkOr_IS_general. The value for the lexical item key is a sorted set of relation ids with their confidence scores.
